.TH man 1 "2018-11-18" "1.3" "vmon man page"
.SH NAME
vmon \- Virtual monitor setup tool.
.SH SYNOPSIS
vmon [help]
.br
     [setup]
.br
     [enable]
.br
     [disable]
.br
.SH DESCRIPTION
vmon is virtual monitor setup tool for Linux.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fBhelp\fP
.br
Print a short help text and exit.
.TP
\fBsetup\fP
.br
Setup profile for virtual monitor.Need to execute each time X server start.
.TP
\fBenable\fP
.br
Enable virtual monitor.
.TP
\fBdisable\fP
.br
Disable virtual monitor.
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
.SH AUTHOR
ChipCE (login721@gmail.com) https://github.com/ChipTechno